name: CUBEICAL - 3D Cube Game
description:
This is a serious challenge between me and you

This is not an easy game to finish in under 30 minutes, Actually this game is harder than you think.

CUBEICAL is basically a sliding cube trying to avoid obstacles in it's way. Yes, It's that simple but can you really beat this game and finish all levels in 30 minutes? I don't think you will. 

How to play this game?

Like any real gamer in this world you will use (W A S D) buttons but you will not use the (W) button because it's a sliding cube and you will not use (S) button because once you start this game there is no stopping or coming back so use A,D to move.
